ThinkPad. I hope that this blog post will help at least one other
person configure Void Linux for mobile research and writing.

Although these notes should be helpful for persons using a
variety of laptop computers for mobile research and writing, they
will be the most immediately relevant for other persons using T-
or X-series Lenovo ThinkPads from the past decade, that is, circa
